{"article_id":"N0AohtNVSQOnyuZ4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The U.S. Army will not ignore any misconduct by released Taliban detainee Sgt . Bowe Bergdahl ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"but he should be considered innocent until proven guilty ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"the chairman of the U.S. Joint Chiefs of Staff said .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"`` The questions about this particular soldier 's conduct are separate from our effort","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to recover ANY U.S. service member in enemy captivity , ''","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"General Martin Dempsey said in a posting on his Facebook page on Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Bergdahl ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"held for nearly five years in Afghanistan ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"was freed last week in a prisoner-swap deal with the Taliban","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"brokered by the Qatari government .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Five Taliban militants were released from the U.S. prison at Guantanamo Bay , Cuba ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and flown to Qatar .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"`` This was likely the last , best opportunity","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"to free him , ''","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Dempsey said .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The general said","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"the military will question Bergdahl about the circumstances of his capture .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"`` Like any American , he is innocent until proven guilty , ''","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Dempsey said .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` Our Army 's leaders will not look away from misconduct","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"if it occurred .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"In the meantime , we will continue to care for him and his family . ''","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Bergdahl was captured in unknown circumstances in eastern Afghanistan on June 30 , 2009 ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"about two months after arriving in the country .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Many U.S. government officials say","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"they believe","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"he was seized","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"after walking away from his unit in violation of U.S. military regulations .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"On Monday , Republican members of the U.S. Congress said","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"President Barack Obama had set a dangerous precedent with the prisoner swap","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"and might have broken the law .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Fueling the criticism were accusations by some soldiers","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"that Bergdahl was a deserter","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"who cost the lives of several comrades .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"Sgt . Bergdahl seems to have grown disillusioned with the mission , bitter about the Army and especially higher ranking enlisted men and officers ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"and simply walked off","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"- gone \" outside the wire \" or protective base limits -","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and disappeared .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"That could indicate","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"that he had gone AWOL","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"( Absence Without Leave ) ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"also referred to as \" Unauthorized Absence \"","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"( UA ) ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"which could bring charges under the Uniform Code of Military Justice","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"( UCMJ ) .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"This scenario","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"- it ' s important to note that it has not been confirmed -","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"is based on detailed reporting in 2012 by Rolling Stone magazine ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"which included interviews with Bergdahl ' s fellow soldiers as well as apparently lengthy conversations with his parents in Idaho ,","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"who shared e-mails","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"they had exchanged with him up until his disappearance .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Obama on Tuesday defended the operation","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"to rescue Bergdahl ,","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"the United States was committed to freeing its prisoners of war","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"regardless of how they were captured .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"On Monday , the State Department said","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"it considered Bergdahl a member of the military","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"who was detained while in combat .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"The Pentagon said","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"it was unable to confirm media reports","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"that troops had been killed","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"trying to locate Bergdahl","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"following his June 2009 disappearance .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"The Pentagon says","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Bergdahl is in a stable condition at the U.S. Army 's Landstuhl Regional Medical Center in Germany ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"where doctors were assessing his condition after five years of captivity .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Officials have indicated","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"there is little desire","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"to pursue any disciplinary action against him","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"given what he has been through .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"( Editing by Doina Chiacu , Lisa Von Ahn and Sofina Mirza-Reid )","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":115,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":110,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":98,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":82,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{